<TEXT>
<P>
   The Kansas City Star plans to move the following additional
story for use by clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and
PMs of Friday, March 19. If you have any questions, please call
Kerry Schmidt on the Star's News Desk at (816) 234-4786.
</P>
<P>
   BASKETBALL-FEVER (Springfield, Mo.) _ College basketball fever
is epidemic in this city, as Southwest Missouri State prepares to
play Duke in the NCAA tournament. By BLAIR KERKHOFF. 2 takes. Story
will move in the ``a'' category.
</P>
