   TRAIN-WRECK (Bourbonnais, Ill.) _ An eyewitness has told
authorities that he saw a truck loaded with steel enter a railroad
crossing despite flashing warning lights just before it was struck
by an onrushing Amtrak passenger train, according to federal
sources. By Bill Dedman.
</P>
