<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-19 14:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6812 &Cx1f; taf-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ACOUSTIC-WEAPONS-(NEW     03-19 0521
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ACOUSTIC-WEAPONS-(NEW-SCIENTIST)-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
NONLETHAL ACOUSTIC WEAPONS SEEM TO BE DOOMED  
 (FOR RELEASE THE WEEK OF MON., MARCH 22, 1999)
</HEADLINE>
   (This article from the London-based science and technology weekly
