<P>
   FLEET-CONSUMERS (Boston) _ Fierce competition between Fleet
Financial Group Inc. and BankBoston Corp. has kept a lid on bank
fees and provided businesses and homebuyers with loan options. A
merger could hurt bank customers. By Kimberly Blanton. 1100 words.
</P>
