<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-19 17:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7057 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NYHAN-COLUMN-$ADV21-B     03-19 1060
