<P>
   BASEBALL
</P>
<P>
   BBN-SOSA _ Sammy Sosa is attacking spring training just like he
attacked the final month of last year: ``Mark McGwire is the man,''
he says. But deep down, Sosa thinks he has another HR record chase
in him. (Pasquarelli, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 20.
</P>
<P>
   COLLEGE BASKETBALL
</P>
<P>
   NCAA MEN'S TOURNAMENT
</P>
<P>
   BKC-NCAARDP _ NCAA tournament roundup story. (Willingham,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   SOUTH REGIONAL
</P>
