</P>
<P>
   BLOOMBERG_Product chronology -- 2 x 20 1/2 --
(BC-BLOOMBERG-NEWS-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Timeline of Bloomberg product development.
</P>
<P>
   BLOOMBERG_Revenue compared -- 1 x 12 -- (BC-BLOOMBERG-NEWS-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Revenue and screen counts of Bloomberg and competitors.
</P>
<P>
   INVEST_Flag Investors -- 1 x 4 1/2 --
(BC-INVEST-WITH-BEHRENS-NYT)
