<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-19 18:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7184 &Cx1f; paxxx
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-STATES-watch-PA     03-19 0830
