<P>
   BKW-NCAA-UCONN (Cincinnati) _ Don't call the Iowa State women's
team the underdogs. That kind of talk drives coach Bill Fennelly
crazy. By Susan Bickelhaupt. 700 words.
</P>
<P>
   BKC-NCAA-RYAN-COLUMN (Knoxville, Tenn.) _ The schedule says the
Celtics are in New York. Don't believe it. The real Celtics will be
on display right here, playing Ohio State. By Bob Ryan.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
