<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-19 19:34 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7272 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OSCARS-NEWCOMERS-LADN     03-19 1312
