<DOCNO> NYT19990319.0429 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-19 23:34 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7631 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-EL-TORO-BATTLE-CRY-EC     03-19 1117
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-EL-TORO-BATTLE-CRY-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
